# TailwindCSS Quick Reference
# This is a quick reference file for TailwindCSS setup in this project

## Project Structure
src/styles/theme.css           → Source CSS with Tailwind directives (tracked in git)
src/styles/_base-theme.css     → Original theme CSS base (tracked in git)
assets/theme.css               → Compiled CSS (auto-generated, don't edit, ignored)
tailwind.config.js             → Tailwind configuration (Preflight disabled)
postcss.config.js              → PostCSS configuration

## Commands
npm run dev-init               → Install all dependencies (first time setup)
npm run dev                    → Start dev server + CSS watch
npm run build                  → Build CSS for production (minified)
npm run css                    → Build CSS once
npm run css:watch              → Watch and rebuild CSS on changes

